| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-5059 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2d156cae-2150-597f-b437-f9a076a9dd5b"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
